name: Sandy Bay Apartments
overview:
Sandy Bay Apartments offer Furnished Apartments in Norfolk VA, Nato housing in Norfolk, furnished short term military apartment housing off base in Norfolk, and off base military Navy housing in Norfolk VA. clients of Sandy Bay are superior to extended stay hotels in Norfolk, VA for guests staying 30 days or more.

Amenities are included in the rental price. Amenities are the following: Off-Street Parking, Cable TV, Microwaves, Air Conditioning, All New Appliances, Laundry Room and Full Kitchen. There are also lots of activities visitors and renters can do. Some of the following are: Biking, Cruises, Sailing, Boating, Fishing, Museums and Swimming.

Every client agrees that it is comparable to extended stay hotel and arming themselves closely for they are not wanting to leave the place anymore. Similar to a dream of living in a comfortable place turning into reality.
